messages.message:
For the new card colors in aihub-uat (https://aihub-uat.internal.instabase.com/) landing page, the current foreground:background contrast ratio for the body text isn't quite right for accessibility
Minimum should be 4.5, ideally 7 (see https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/Understanding_WCAG/Perceivable/Color_contrast)

Current is 3.36 and 4.31. It was 6.63 in the previous one

This needs some work before going out... have we done any design review on this

Let's chat tomorrow, don't think the new homepage is ready for a public release yet cc @Eric Han
I used a design from the design team. alagu is out this week. Who should we get a review from?
